athlete|{{sortname|Bobby|Jones|dab=golfer}} (a)|USA}}\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|[[1926 Open Championship|1926]], [[1927 Open Championship|1927]], [[1930 Open Championship|1930]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |{{flagathlete|{{sortname|Henry|Cotton|dab=golfer}}|ENG}}\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|[[1934 Open Championship|1934]], [[1937 Open Championship|1937]], [[1948 Open Championship|1948]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |{{flagathlete|{{sortname|Gary|Player}}|RSA}}\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|[[1959 Open Championship|1959]], [[1968 Open Championship|1968]], [[1974 Open Championship|1974]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |{{flagathlete|{{sortname|Jack|Nicklaus}}|USA}}\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|[[1966 Open Championship|1966]], [[1970 Open Championship|1970]], [[1978 Open Championship|1978]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |{{flagathlete|{{sortname|Seve|Ballesteros}}|ESP}}\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|[[1979 Open Championship|1979]], [[1984 Open Championship|1984]], [[1988 Open Championship|1988]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |{{flagathlete|{{sortname|Nick|Faldo}}|ENG}}\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|[[1987 Open Championship|1987]], [[1990 Open Championship|1990]], [[1992 Open Championship|1992]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |{{flagathlete|{{sortname|Tiger|Woods}}|USA}}\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|[[2000 Open Championship|2000]], [[2005 Open Championship|2005]], [[2006 Open Championship|2006]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |{{flagathlete|{{sortname|Bob|Martin|dab=golfer}}|SCO}}\n|align=\"center\"|2\n|[[1876 Open Championship|1876]], [[1885 Open Championship|1885]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |{{flagathlete|{{sortname|Willie|Park Jr.||Park, Willie Jr.}}|SCO}}\n|align=\"center\"|2\n|[[1887 Open Championship|1887]], [[1889 Open Championship|1889]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |{{flagathlete|{{sortname|Harold|Hilton}} (a)|ENG}}\n|align=\"center\"|2\n|[[1892 Open Championship|1892]], [[1897 Open Championship|1897]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |{{flagathlete|{{sortname|Arnold|Palmer}}|USA}}\n|align=\"center\"|2\n|[[1961 Open Championship|1961]], [[1962 Open Championship|1962]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\